For Screaming Vlog 36 we meet up with @salba69, @twistthewrist, @jake_wooten, and @catchsurf Pros @kalanirobb, @johnnyredmond, and @tylerstanaland at Catch Surf HQ in Encinitas, CA! After drying off from the water, we go from the waves to the 'crete as the squad heads to Poods Park to catch a session before calling it a day! Hit up our @youtube channel to watch now! For Screaming Vlog 35 we meet up with @tomasta, @k3vinbraun, @maurcoy, @jeremeknibbs, and SC Team Manager @instapizzle in San Diego while we keep the hype train rollin' celebrating @jake_wooten’s long awaited PRO status. From skating flat ground straight to the vert ramp, we gather the squad and head out to @tonyhawk’s compound to get some serious shredding dialed in. We got @twistthewrist, @ericdressen and @blood_wizard Pro @tweestopher in the mix to get things fired up while the gang hits every inch of The Birdman’s indoor skatepark! Where should we go in the next Screaming Vlog? Let us know in the comments!

If there is one thing we are certain of, it's that @ericdressen knows skateboarding. From going pro in 1987 for DogTown Skates, to becoming one of the biggest names in legendary style, Dressen has acquired a fine taste in skateboarding. When Eric first met @misugu0228, he had guessed she was on the Santa Cruz International team from all of her SC gear. When Eric learned Misugu was buying it all, he immediately called SC Brand Manager @andrewcannon and then @rictawheels Brand Manager @stroullos to make some calls and get Misugu properly hooked up! Misugu has since gone on to become a World Champion winning eight titles IN A ROW! Join Misugu and Eric D as they tell their tale of blossoming friendship, epic skateboarding, and lending a helping hand. 

👉 Misugu's setup:
8.0 VX Deck
139 Independent Trucks
56mm Ricta Wheels
Bronson Bearings
Mob Grip 🎯
Hit our @youtube channel to watch now!
🎥: @trevarcushing 
🎬: @ericdanescu 
#SantaCruzSkateboards
